The paper focuses on using convolutional neural networks for image classification and level-set algorithm for tumor segmentation in mammography images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories. Additionally, since the paper deals with medical imaging, cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible sub-category. Finally, since the paper involves image processing and segmentation, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible sub-category.
